description: The bronze pieces are the "first real evidence" Viking women visited the Isle of Man, an expert says.
title: 'Significant' Isle of Man Viking brooches declared treasure
title_page: 'Significant' Isle of Man Viking brooches declared treasure - BBC News
maintext: "It was always a mystery why we hadn't found [such artefacts] on the Isle of Man, so that's why these two brooches are so significant."
